---
title: HelloHero: Texan Beef Rump & Root Veggie Medley with Baby Leaves & Smokey Aioli
description: Get the bold flavours of American cuisine right in your kitchen! Just coat beef rump with our All-American spice blend, roast a chunky veggie toss and dollop smokey aioli over the whole shebang.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
